verbose_text: Previously reported studies have shown that the expression of ASH1L inhibited interleukin-6 (IL-6) and toll like receptor (TLR) that triggered the production of tumor necrosis factor (TNF) in a mouse model of sepsis [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: interleukin-6 (IL-6) and toll-like receptor (TLR) that triggered the production of tumor necrosis factor
